reviews.text: They have improved a lotttt. I used to hate this place but their sushi are fresh! However it is quite expensive now but if they can keep this quality I am happy to visit them again.

It's a nice little place. A big chain, so you can get more or less the same stuff everywhere. I like that there is a good variety of fish and types of sushi here. Pretty comfy place, and good quality sushi.
Affordable sushi of decent quality.
Got horrendous food poisoning from expired raw squid. Puked three times at the restaurant and through the night. They still made me pay the bill. You get 10% off if they poison you.
Price is reasonable and food is fresh.

result.name: 板長壽司

reviews.text:
壽司”有骨

同單叫一件“海膽軍艦”，另外一件係“北海道海膽壽司”。重點係一件有紫菜包住，另一件係冇既。點知“冇包紫菜”個件未黎，就示意服務員跟進下，接住個服務員就大大聲話出左比我地，咁我地冇食到當然同佢爭論啦。
個男服務員話：算啦，我同師傅都記得整左比你，唔緊要，整過比你地。
服務差，食物有骨，仲要做錯唔認。間野等執啦！
其實真的一般，選擇不多價格又不便宜。
They have improved a lotttt. I used to hate this place but their sushi are fresh! However it is quite expensive now but if they can keep this quality I am happy to visit them again.

It's a nice little place. A big chain, so you can get more or less the same stuff everywhere. I like that there is a good variety of fish and types of sushi here. Pretty comfy place, and good quality sushi.
同一個集團不同分店，壽司份量超細，見意不要去此分店。
